<s docid="FBIS3-59723" num="113"> (3) Exhaust Gas Performance Figure 15 shows the relationship between NOx and excess air ratio (\|[lgr ]\|) at 1,500 rpm and respective loads of P\|[lt ]\|inf\|[gt ]\| e\|[lt ]\|/inf\|[gt ]\| =0.1 MPa and P\|[lt ]\|inf\|[gt ]\| e\|[lt ]\|/inf\|[gt ]\| =0.29 MPa.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-59723" num="114"> For P\|[lt ]\|inf\|[gt ]\| e\|[lt ]\|/inf\|[gt ]\| =0.1 MPa, NOx are nearly zero above \|[lgr ]\|=1.5; and for P\|[lt ]\|inf\|[gt ]\| e\|[lt ]\|/inf\|[gt ]\| =0.29 MPa, nearly zero above \|[lgr ]\|=2.0.</s>
